{"tid":2373332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗稱已接種國藥疫苗　並要求盡快供應國產疫苗到港","createTime":"2021-01-20T11:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T12:11:04.000Z","uid":241764,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9da175044b0a66b764ff528300d49aff11cc08","tid":2373332,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"正在北京出席全國人大常委會會議的常委譚耀宗表示，今天已經接種第一劑的國藥新冠病毒疫苗，暫時未有特別反應，日後可在北京或者深圳接種第二劑疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗透露，出席3月全國兩會的人大及政協，可能參與接種疫苗，但未清楚是否強制執行。他認為，接種疫苗是好事，可以在大會舉行期間提供多一重保障。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571442-20210120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571442-20210120.htm&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Iax5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=14a4041c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571442-20210120.htm&h=7c205e5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571442-20210120.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n應該無機會接種第二劑了 RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1a5e7ce4cbd44cdd9199953fe6258196c7c22f","tid":2373332,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"佢話係就係？打左咩邊個知"},{"pid":"57b9a08ae2d5797784ee5971891abc0f4473a2ef","tid":2373332,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"可能只係俾人打咗懵仔針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcc6c2339e0b2d40c9ec0bbf8d76f02468387ab","tid":2373332,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:19:49.000Z","msg":"美國制裁吓你姐 廢老譚唔駛搞到去自殺咁大件事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e678e986e4d738a491fd39e76cbe317b5e610e","tid":2373332,"uid":35514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d1a5e7ce4cbd44cdd9199953fe6258196c7c22f","tid":2373332,"uid":12628,"like"